### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8001

### ============================================================
### CATEGORY 8 — Cancellation Errors (cancel_id)
### ============================================================

### Successful cancellation (expect 200)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/fhir/r4/ServiceRequest/ORDER-123

### ERR-NOT-PROPAGATED → 200 with propagated=false
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/fhir/r4/ServiceRequest/ERR-NOT-PROPAGATED

### ERR-PROCESSING → 409 OperationOutcome
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/fhir/r4/ServiceRequest/ERR-PROCESSING

### ERR-RESULT-ISSUED → 422 OperationOutcome
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/fhir/r4/ServiceRequest/ERR-RESULT-ISSUED

### ERR-PARTIAL-CANCEL → 207 partial cancel
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/fhir/r4/ServiceRequest/ERR-PARTIAL-CANCEL

### ============================================================
### End-to-end scenario — contest demo priority #4
### ============================================================

### Step 1: POST clean ServiceRequest (expect 201)
POST {{baseUrl}}/fhir/r4/ServiceRequest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resourceType": "ServiceRequest",
  "subject": { "reference": "Patient/PAC-001" },
  "code": { "coding": [{ "code": "HEM-001" }] }
}

### Step 2: DELETE the order (expect 409 — already processing)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/fhir/r4/ServiceRequest/ERR-PROCESSING
